interactions. Furthermore, we find that we can describe all studied vortex\nlattices within a single framework consisting of a continous deviation from\nhyperuniformity towards random distributions when increasing the strength of\npinning with respect to the intervortex interaction.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 24 Feb 2020 19:48:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-29"}
