ally\ntailored simulation configuration does not conflict with the systems\nperiodicity and provides substantially more realistic total elastic energies at\nhigh precipitate volume fractions. The energetically most favorable\nsuperstructure is found to be a hexagonal precipitate arrangement.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Feb 2020 12:11:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-26"}
